Volume 1 - Preamble

[Hello reader! This is the source code for the Spring Thing 2021 release of The Weight of a Soul. It's provided as a teaching tool for new Inform writers and a case study for those trying to get more out of the Inform 7 engine. I've done my best to add comments in the code to make it easier to read and understand.

As with most large projects, this source text has accumulated a bit of spaghetti code and black magic to get the whole thing working. I've forked this public release from an in-development build and cleaned it up to the best of my ability, but you will still see lots of unlabeled rules, unoptimized rulebooks, etc.

Finally, it should go without saying that this source text contains MASSIVE SPOILERS for The Weight of a Soul. If you don't want to be spoiled, stop reading now and finish playing the game!]

