Understand "wave hello" or "wave hello [text]" or "wave goodbye" or "wave goodbye [text]" as a mistake ("[generic TALK TO tutorial]"). [Because OF COURSE wxd tried this]

Instead of asking someone to try doing something, say generic TALK TO tutorial.
Instead of answering someone that something, say generic TALK TO tutorial.

